show.description: When superstar actor Ben reaches the pinnacle of his career, everything he's worked for suddenly hangs in the balance. As rumors swirl about his relationship with another famous male celebrity, the industry's unforgiving spotlight threatens to derail his carefully crafted image. Desperate to protect his career, Ben makes a decision that will entangle him in an elaborate charade. How far will he go to maintain his public persona when his private life becomes headline news?
